Cell["\<\
The simulation picks up the exact solution.  This has the characteristics of \
a second-order phase transition (the order parameter changes continuously \
across the critical temperature). However, in a finite system, even a first \
order transition would have this continuous behavior\[LongDash]so, our result \
is not necessarily evidence that the order-disorder transition is first or \
second order.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9937338490009727`*^9, 3.993733900262847*^9}, {
  3.99373405942269*^9, 
  3.9937341538520947`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"36951037-bc10-476a-b649-\
c16da33280d6"]
}, Open  ]]
}, Open  ]],

